{
  "stem": "3855.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "How he built himself up again is another story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I just want to show you, in no way did this man send his money out to Switzerland, anticipating anything like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Even after '33, thinking that-- and this was in the Sudetenland, where my father was born, where the German language was the language and where the German influence was very predominant-- and yet, this thought never entered our mind.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It only started to enter our mind and everybody's mind, I'm venturing to say, when Austria was invaded.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was then all of a sudden that we got shaken up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Because little by little, the terrorizing of the population took very subtle forms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They picked up Jews and had them wash the sidewalk-- older people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "These type of things, little by little, made one realize that-- that-- that there's-- there's a different world coming along.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And it was then that everybody scrambled to put their registration number down at the various consulates.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We had relatives, my father and my mother, particularly my mother, had outstanding relatives in the United States.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I will mention it later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "When-- so we wrote to them for affidavits.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we registered, of course, with the United States consulate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But in those days, there was the quota system.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "The quota system was based upon the-- the numerical composition of the citizens of the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It was so many from Germany, and so few from Czechoslovakia, and so many from Italy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And according to that, a certain number were permitted to come here, and the reason was given according to availability.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Now, Austria and Germany had a good quota.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Czechoslovakia was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
